DUGGAN MCDONNELL:
Hits you right there.

00:21:06.750 --> 00:21:07.375
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:21:07.375 --> 00:21:08.750
DUGGAN MCDONNELL:
So you had two.

00:21:08.750 --> 00:21:09.540
That's great.

