00:21:19.520 --> 00:21:21.080
All right.

00:21:21.080 --> 00:21:21.580
Sure.

00:21:21.580 --> 00:21:25.400
The question is, can I name
a few local rye whiskys.

00:21:25.400 --> 00:21:29.750
So in addition to
Anchor, the folks

00:21:29.750 --> 00:21:32.210
